    "description": "Always shock. Increased damage, magazine size and projectile size. Fires slow-moving bolts that accelerate; after a set distance they become invisible. Each bolt ricochets off the first surface it hits, then detonates on impact to deal splash damage in a small radius. The explosion deals 70% of weapon damage as splash and is increased by grenade damage bonuses. Hyperion trait: sustained fire improves accuracy and reduces recoil."
